The paper presents a distributed algorithm for approximating a minimum weight vertex cover in hypergraphs, which is a problem in distributed computing and graph theory. Therefore, cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are the most likely categories. The paper also involves information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Additionally, the paper discusses integer covering-programs, which is a topic in computational complexity (cs.CC).
